        "name": "image_edit",
        "description": "Edit or transform existing image(s) via the xAI Imagine API; use instead of image_gen for image-to-image work (preserve likeness, transfer style, remix). Returns the saved image's absolute path. Each required `image` is one reference, in priority order: (1) a user attachment — pass its placeholder token, e.g. \"[Image #1]\" (attachments have no path you can see, so never invent one); (2) an absolute filesystem path the user gave you; (3) a `data:image/...;base64,...` URL. Example: image_edit(prompt=\"colorize this\", image=[\"[Image #1]\"]) or image_edit(prompt=\"this person in the style of retro anime cowboy bebop\", image=[\"/Users/kgeorge/Downloads/profile.jpg\"])",
